# Chapter 3 — Keras and Data Retrieval in TensorFlow 2

This chapter introduces the three Keras model–building APIs and explains how
TensorFlow retrieves, processes, and prepares datasets for machine learning
pipelines. The concepts are presented in the same structure and order as the
original book.

---

